tip.text: V welcoming feel the moment I stepped in. Love how cosy it is, friendly staffs, yummy waffle! Waffle seems to have a tinge of orange flavour which makes it unique! Free wifi 1234567890! ;)
All food items on menu off 50%! Apparently it was due to the pre- opening promotion! Heard fr waiter it has been so since March! Not sure when the promo is ending. Decent food n cheap beer! :)
